General.Name: Inission AB (publ)
General.Description: Inission AB (publ) engages in the supply of tailored manufacturing services and products in the field of industrial electronics and mechanics in Sweden, Finland, Estonia, Norway, the United States, and internationally. It offers contract manufacturing of electronics and mechanics under the Inission brand, covering the entire product lifecycle, including development, design, industrialization, volume production, and aftermarket services. The company, through its subsidiaries, is also involved in the development, manufacture, and sale of electronic power supplies and system solutions under the Enedo brand. It serves defense, electrification, marine technology, LED display, automation, test and instruments, communication and IoT, MedTech, and other Industries. The company was founded in 1973 and is based in Karlstad, Sweden.
